subproject.corporate outcome: Strengthened capacities of national human rights institutions
subproject.description:
Output 1: PMU established to render technical advice and coordinate the attainment of the identified outputs.
Output 2: Strengthen professional standards and economic viability of Media Houses to advocate for human development 
Output 3: Capacity of Civil Society organizations strengthened to monitor and respond to Economic and Political Decisions taken at National and Local level 
Output 4: Policy and legal environment enhanced for protection of Human Rights and greater civic participation in the economic and political decision-making process
Output 5: Strengthened and increased participation of CSOs/NGOs in the National AIDs  response
subproject.gender code: Gender equality as a significant objective
subproject.title: UNDEF MEDIA & CSO CAPACITY BUI
